verses.verse: The Lord <S%H3068><s%> reigns, <S%H4427><s%> He is clothed <S%H3847><s%> with majesty; <S%H1348><s%> The Lord <S%H3068><s%> has clothed <S%H3847><s%> and girded <S%H247><s%> Himself with strength; <S%H5797><s%> Indeed, <S%H637><s%> the world <S%H8398><s%> is firmly <S%H3559><s%> established, <S%H3559><s%> it will not be moved. <S%H4131><s%>
Thy throne <S%H3678><s%> is established <S%H3559><s%> from of old; <S%H9241><s%> Thou art from everlasting. <S%H5769><s%>

More <S%H4480><s%> than <S%H4480><s%> the sounds <S%H6963><s%> of many <S%H7227><s%> waters, <S%H4325><s%> [Than] the mighty <S%H117><s%> breakers <S%H4867><s%> of the sea, <S%H3220><s%> The Lord <S%H3068><s%> on high <S%H4791><s%> is mighty. <S%H117><s%>

Thy testimonies <S%H9381><s%> are fully <S%H3966><s%> confirmed; <S%H539><s%> Holiness <S%H6944><s%> befits <S%H4998><s%> Thy house, <S%H1004><s%> O Lord, <S%H3068><s%> forevermore. <S%H753><s%> <S%H3117><s%>
